{"tid":2351532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國據報允讓民眾接種兩劑不同公司生產的疫苗","createTime":"2021-01-03T09:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T16:33:20.000Z","uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1739b915386cfab1b0c73babdcb8548678336aee","tid":2351532,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568294-20210102.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568294-20210102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0Ng1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=0c1117a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568294-20210102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6d0d8c8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568294-20210102.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亦有報道指，政府修改疫苗接種指引，如果供應不足，第二劑疫苗可以用另一間公司生產的疫苗替代，牴觸美國疾控中心有關疫苗不可互換的指引，因為接種不同疫苗的安全性和有效性，未經評估。有專家批評，英國官員似乎完全放棄科學。英國目前已經批准使用輝瑞與BioNTech，以及牛津與阿斯利康研發的疫苗。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/afa31d12-c393-402b-9677-1fb312cfa1cf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2Fafa31d12-c393-402b-9677-1fb312cfa1cf&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0Ng1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=3334829c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/afa31d12-c393-402b-9677-1fb312cfa1cf</a><br />\n<br />\nThe UK has drawn up plans that would allow patients to be given different coronavirus vaccines for the first and second doses under certain circumstances, a move that highlights a widening rift in public health policy between the UK and rest of the West.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n願主保佑<br />\n溝藥食都未必安全<br />\n溝疫苗打???<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"